      • getFolderSize

        public Long getFolderSize(long id,
                          String filter,
                          boolean visibleOnly)
        Retrieves the count of the number of contents in the folder. Currently, it is assumed that the contents of folders are only entries. The entries that are counted are those that have a visibility of "OK"
        Parameters:
        id - unique folder identifier
        filter - optional filter for entry fields
        visibleOnly - if true, counts only entries with visibility "OK"
        Returns:
        number of child contents in the folder

      • getFolderContentIds

        public List<Long> getFolderContentIds(long folderId,
                                      EntryType type,
                                      boolean visibleOnly)
        Retrieves the ids of any entries that are contained in the specified folder; optionally filtered by entry type
        Parameters:
        folderId - unique folder identifier
        type - optional filter for entries. If null, all entries will be retrieved
        Returns:
        List of entry ids found in the folder with the filter applied if applicable and which have a visibility of "OK"

      • retrieveFolderContents

                                          PageParameters pageParameters,
                                          boolean visibleOnly)
        Retrieves list of entries that conforms to the parameters
        Parameters:

        pageParameters - paging params
        visibleOnly - whether to only include entries with "OK" visibility
        Returns:
        list of found entries
        Throws:
        DAOException - on HibernateException retrieving
